# Älvsutloppet Timing System

A desktop application for managing race timing, runner registration, result export, prize draws, high score lists, and a public display window for the Älvsutloppet race event.

Built with C++ and Qt Widgets.

## Features

- Runner registration with start number, name, category, track, and birth year
- Race timer with finish registration
- Undo support for removed finish times
- Autosave using JSON to protect data if the program closes unexpectedly
- CSV export of results
- Prize draw system for different runner categories
- High score/top list display
- Separate public display window intended for a second screen

